#: ../../language/error_codes/E0074.md:1
msgid "E0074"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0074.md:3
msgid "Warning name: `missing_doc`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0074.md:5
msgid "Public declaration is missing documentation."
msgstr "公开声明缺少文档。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0074.md:7
msgid ""
"When documentation checking is enabled, public declarations should have a"
" docstring starting with `///`. This keeps generated API documentation "
"useful for downstream users."
msgstr ""
"启用文档检查时，公开声明应当带有以 `///` 开头的文档字符串。"
"这样生成的 API 文档才能对下游用户有用。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0074.md:11
msgid "Erroneous example"
msgstr "错误示例"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0074.md:13
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"pub fn exposed() -> Int {\n"
"  1\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"test {\n"
"  inspect(exposed(), content=\"1\")\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0074.md:17
msgid "Suggestion"
msgstr "建议"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0074.md:19
msgid "Add a docstring above the public declaration."
msgstr "在公开声明上方添加文档字符串。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0074.md:21
msgid ""
"/// Returns a stable value for the example.\n"
"pub fn exposed() -> Int {\n"
"  1\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"test {\n"
"  inspect(exposed(), content=\"1\")\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""
